  "body": "## What's Changed\r\n* Update error message to be more verbose by @vihu in https://github.com/schollz/croc/pull/682\r\n* Gracefully handle non existend receive config file by @a1lu in https://github.com/schollz/croc/pull/685\r\n* Check $HOME as last by @a1lu in https://github.com/schollz/croc/pull/684\r\n* Support spaces in 4 word codes by @a1lu in https://github.com/schollz/croc/pull/683\r\n* Avoid to create config dir if not required by @a1lu in https://github.com/schollz/croc/pull/686\r\n* Bump golang.org/x/net from 0.22.0 to 0.23.0 by @dependabot in https://github.com/schollz/croc/pull/687\r\n* Bump golang.org/x/crypto from 0.21.0 to 0.22.0 by @dependabot in https://github.com/schollz/croc/pull/688\r\n\r\n## New Contributors\r\n* @vihu made their first contribution in https://github.com/schollz/croc/pull/682\r\n* @a1lu made their first contribution in https://github.com/schollz/croc/pull/685\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/schollz/croc/compare/v9.6.14...v9.6.15",
